snippet.title: The Way Home 1.0
snippet.description:
It is a rogue-like dungeon crawler game. Trapped on an island with a strange cave, Kevin and Cheese struggle to return home. Defeat enemies, collect resources, and construct buildings. You can enjoy dynamic battles with the cuteness of pixel art.
